description: Fighting between Armenia and Azerbaijan over the disputed enclave has escalated in recent days.
title: In pictures: Fighting rages in Nagorno-Karabakh conflict
title_page: In pictures: Fighting rages in Nagorno-Karabakh conflict - BBC News
maintext: There are fears that the actual death toll among the militaries from all sides as well as civilians could be much higher, as casualty claims have not been independently verified.
